Description: Un-hardcode CMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX in CMakeLists.txt
 The upstream CMakeLists.txt sets CMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX to /usr, which
 conflicts with dh_auto_configure's --prefix flag. Comment out the
 hardcoded line so dh can set the prefix.
Author: pistomp <pistomp@example.com>
Forwarded: not-needed
Last-Update: 2026-06-22

--- a/CMakeLists.txt
+++ b/CMakeLists.txt
@@ -1,4 +1,4 @@
-set(CMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX /usr)
+# set(CMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX /usr)
```

